(sudden hubbub)

21:41.359 --> 21:42.858
- Move!
- Thank you.

21:42.860 --> 21:46.119
Just a minute, counselor.
(gavel banging)
Order!

21:46.197 --> 21:47.788
- You're in my spot.

21:47.807 --> 21:49.865
(gavel banging)
Order in this court!

21:49.884 --> 21:54.294
Now this is a public trial,
you are allowed to be here.

21:54.314 --> 21:57.148
But I will not tolerate
any further disruption.

21:57.375 --> 21:59.483
Do you recognize any of them?

21:59.635 --> 22:01.393
- No.
(man): What's your problem?

22:01.470 --> 22:04.030
- Please continue, counselor.

22:05.232 --> 22:07.900
- This case is about violence,

22:08.052 --> 22:11.037
lethal violence.

22:16.652 --> 22:18.669
(admirative whistling)

22:19.839 --> 22:21.672
- I told you.
She's perfect.

22:21.824 --> 22:24.157
- Yeah, where'd you learn
to shoot like that?

22:24.235 --> 22:26.251
Oh, um, Quantico.

22:26.404 --> 22:28.012
- What?

22:28.163 --> 22:30.664
- East Tennessee.

22:30.683 --> 22:34.760
- So you two just old friends
from there?

22:34.912 --> 22:38.171
- Uh, no, not really.
- Where then?

22:38.265 --> 22:41.192
- Uh, well, it was after
the "incident" in Brooklyn.

22:41.343 --> 22:43.677
The hysteria down there
was off the charts.

22:43.738 --> 22:47.365
Everyone screaming about the
violence, and the violence.

22:47.441 --> 22:50.034
The violence they brought on
themselves by the way.

22:50.761 --> 22:54.613
It was making me crazy
so I was in need of
some adult conversation

22:54.765 --> 22:59.126
and uh, miraculously
this gentleman appeared.

22:59.954 --> 23:01.879
- Why do you live there?

23:02.698 --> 23:05.049
- Not everyone can live here
in Valhalla.

23:05.126 --> 23:06.366
- Yeah, good point.

23:06.386 --> 23:09.202
