would it?

23:12.299 --> 23:14.875
- Well, there's something
you can't say out loud, right?

23:14.952 --> 23:15.968
- Why not?

23:16.044 --> 23:19.138
I don't mind the blacks,
I love 'em.

23:19.232 --> 23:22.048
As long as they're in Africa.

23:22.068 --> 23:24.126
Mexicans in Mexico.

23:24.219 --> 23:25.978
Jews in Israel.

23:26.072 --> 23:28.464
Let them have
their so-called culture,

23:28.482 --> 23:31.409
just don't come here
and mess up ours.

23:32.078 --> 23:35.137
And now suddenly
we're the terrorists?

23:35.156 --> 23:37.489
