you know what they'd call it...

23:47.944 --> 23:49.367
they'd call it genocide.

23:49.429 --> 23:52.655
So anything that we do
in response,

23:52.657 --> 23:55.248
that's called self-defense.

23:55.268 --> 23:58.510
(Essie): Yeah.
- What are you clowns doin'?

23:58.587 --> 24:00.179
- Tryin' to make the world
a better place.

24:00.331 --> 24:01.939
- C'mon.
I need your help.

24:02.090 --> 24:03.941
- Now?
