24:29.376 --> 24:32.094
He said they're
working on something?

24:32.972 --> 24:34.880
- A little surprise party.

24:35.032 --> 24:36.682
- Uh...

24:40.128 --> 24:41.795
Um, I've got to pee.

24:41.814 --> 24:44.631
- Just past the kitchen.
On the left.

24:44.709 --> 24:45.816
- Great.

24:45.968 --> 24:48.527
(door opening)

24:55.736 --> 24:58.579
(soft music)

25:57.965 --> 26:00.140
