26:18.803 --> 26:20.226
- Esme?

26:20.246 --> 26:22.746
- I knew I recognized you.

26:25.585 --> 26:27.142
Give me your phone.

26:27.161 --> 26:29.645
- I don't want to.

26:29.663 --> 26:32.464
- Give me your phone.

26:38.172 --> 26:40.180
What's the passcode?

26:41.992 --> 26:45.144
Punch in the passcode.

26:48.833 --> 26:50.423
Do it yourself.

26:50.443 --> 26:53.018
- Punch in the code!
(Esme panting)

26:53.095 --> 26:55.487
- Okay. Okay.

27:05.199 --> 27:07.458
- You disgust me.

27:13.115 --> 27:15.591
(crashing)

27:22.642 --> 27:27.035
