27:38.491 --> 27:41.307
(phone beeps)
Now she's said "be careful"

27:41.327 --> 27:43.886
and I'm going to respond.

27:43.904 --> 27:45.570
Thumbs up.

27:45.665 --> 27:47.239
Pink heart.
Purple heart.

27:47.315 --> 27:50.058
Is there an emoji
for "race traitor"? Hmm?

27:50.060 --> 27:52.169
There should be.

27:54.322 --> 27:56.415
- What are we going
to do with her?

27:56.567 --> 27:58.567
Not a lot of options, now,
are there?

27:58.585 --> 28:01.345
- I won't tell anyone. I swear.
- And why would we believe you?

28:01.422 --> 28:04.072
