I couldn't stand it anymore.

28:49.303 --> 28:51.787
So I started my engine.

28:52.398 --> 28:55.290
And you know
what happened next.

28:55.292 --> 28:57.550
- No, please.
I won't tell anyone.

28:57.570 --> 28:59.962
I won't say a word.
Please, please.

28:59.980 --> 29:01.221
- You got that right.

29:01.223 --> 29:02.406
- Dude, you kill a white girl

29:02.557 --> 29:04.057
