in our law enforcement
all of a sudden.

29:08.230 --> 29:10.063
- I swear. I swear.
Please, please.

29:10.140 --> 29:13.308
- She doesn't know our names,
we can just leave her here
and get lost.

29:13.310 --> 29:15.978
- She likes girls,
you get that, right?

29:15.996 --> 29:18.589
- We've got enough heat on us
as it is, thanks to you.

29:18.740 --> 29:19.831
- Thanks to me?
- Yeah.

29:19.908 --> 29:21.483
- You're the moron
who brought her here,

29:21.485 --> 29:24.911
so unless you want to man up
and take care of this,

29:24.930 --> 29:26.430
get outta my face.

29:26.432 --> 29:30.434
(Esme, panting): No.
Please, please, please.

29:31.145 --> 29:34.062
(groaning)
(rod tinkling)

29:37.960 --> 29:40.360
(Esme whimpering)

29:43.098 --> 29:45.407
(ripping sound)
- Ah!

29:46.786 --> 29:48.786
Ah, no, no!

29:48.937 --> 29:50.621
- The car! Go!

29:54.852 --> 29:56.710
(panting)

29:58.464 --> 30:00.022
(crashing)

30:00.040 --> 30:02.591
(engine starting)

30:11.535 --> 30:14.061
(phone buzzing)

30:15.130 --> 30:16.462
- Hey, baby.

30:16.540 --> 30:18.965
<i>I've been worried. Are you okay?</i>
- I have the car,

30:18.984 --> 30:20.425
the one that hit Jordan.
- What?

30:20.502 --> 30:22.878
<i> - I'm driving it now.</i>
- Where are you?

30:22.896 --> 30:24.988
- Upstate, near Arden.

30:25.065 --> 30:26.398
Uh, the driver's there.

30:26.492 --> 30:29.051
It's a farm with a white house
and two barns.

30:29.053 --> 30:30.661
- Essie, are you okay?

30:30.812 --> 30:33.388
The FBI and the police
need to get there,
so you need to call them.

30:33.407 --> 30:35.557
<i> - Alright.</i>
<i> It's going to be okay.</i>

30:35.559 --> 30:37.960
- He tried to kill me.

30:43.567 --> 30:47.419
- The People call
Aaliyah Williams to the stand.

30:47.571 --> 30:50.597
(men cough and boo)

30:53.243 --> 30:55.853
- I will have order
in this court!

30:56.004 --> 30:59.748
I repeat, I will have order
in this court.

30:59.750 --> 31:02.359
Bailiff, remove these people.
(coughing continues)

31:02.510 --> 31:05.404
Bailiff, clear the court!
(gavel banging)

31:06.031 --> 31:09.074
(struggling sounds)

31:12.872 --> 31:14.746
(soft music)

31:19.027 --> 31:21.753
(sirens wailing)

31:34.451 --> 31:36.727
(panting)

31:38.397 --> 31:40.138
(Esme crying)

31:40.215 --> 31:42.357
- It's okay. It's okay.

31:56.323 --> 31:59.124
It's okay.
I'm right here.

32:06.574 --> 32:08.634
- Everybody back!

32:30.598 --> 32:33.024
- They're almost done.

32:33.101 --> 32:34.618
- Did they find anything?

32:34.769 --> 32:37.012
- No, it didn't sound like it.

32:37.790 --> 32:41.792
Apparently the owner is
some old guy in a nursing home
in New Jersey.

32:41.868 --> 32:43.276
- What?

32:43.295 --> 32:46.129
He didn't even know
anyone was living here.

32:49.359 --> 32:51.359
You cannot blame yourself
for what happened.

32:51.361 --> 32:53.804
- Who else is there to blame?

32:53.880 --> 32:55.621
- I mean...

32:56.049 --> 32:58.366
I started this whole thing.
- No.

32:58.385 --> 33:00.869
- I feel like I got us
into this.

33:00.887 --> 33:03.105
- No, it's not the same.

33:04.374 --> 33:07.375
(mumbling nervously)
Do they have any ideas?

33:07.394 --> 33:10.212
Like where to find these people?
Or where they might have gone?

33:10.230 --> 33:12.805
Or...
anything at all?

33:13.734 --> 33:15.808
- They said they think
they're from out of state.

33:15.886 --> 33:17.518
- Wait, wait... what?
If they're...

33:17.663 --> 33:19.904
okay, if they're
from out of state, how did
they know about this place?

33:19.999 --> 33:22.741
- I don't know.
- How did they know
that nobody was living here?

33:22.743 --> 33:26.336
