33:31.752 --> 33:33.510
Okay?

33:36.015 --> 33:38.098
Let's go home.

33:40.927 --> 33:42.427
- Yeah.

33:43.188 --> 33:46.064
Yeah, um, I'll be up there
in a minute, okay?

33:47.934 --> 33:49.693
- Alright.

34:21.209 --> 34:23.435
(camera clicking)

34:36.133 --> 34:37.240
<i> (Esme): Hi.</i>

34:37.317 --> 34:39.317
- Hey, baby.
