35:27.459 --> 35:29.209
I love you.

35:29.870 --> 35:31.586
- I love you too.

35:42.199 --> 35:45.058
(phone ringing)

35:49.890 --> 35:51.356
- Hey.

35:51.799 --> 35:53.041
Aaliyah?

35:53.059 --> 35:55.527
- You lied to me.

35:56.897 --> 35:58.137
