36:14.564 --> 36:16.915
<i>(Esme): We're fine, we're fine.</i>

36:17.067 --> 36:18.750
<i> I promise, okay.</i>

36:18.844 --> 36:20.594
<i> We're fine.</i>

36:21.254 --> 36:23.405
- I love you, Essie.

36:23.998 --> 36:26.558
<i> I mean, you know that, right?</i>

36:28.929 --> 36:31.062
(phone ringing)

36:34.526 --> 36:36.100
<i> (Aaliyah): Essie?</i>

36:36.695 --> 36:39.771
