36:49.266 --> 36:51.583
<i> Hmm?</i>
<i> What are you going to do?</i>

36:54.046 --> 36:56.120
I want to come help you, okay?

36:56.197 --> 36:58.548
- No, I don't want you involved.

36:58.700 --> 37:01.718
